headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Discounts
content:
All High-End Apartments are 30% off. Then visit your local Ammu-Nation to purchase Carbine and Assault Rifles and all their customization options for 50% off. Plus, there are a range of cars on sale this week, including:

- Vapid Dominator GTT - 30% off
- Vulcar Warrener HKR – 30% off
- Annis Remus – 30% off
- Dinka Jester RR – 40% off

Head to the LS Car Meet to tune up your purchased vehicle or go to the Modding Bay of the Auto Shop.

Check out the Rockstar Newswire for more details.
